    <description>
'SoilMod' adds custom growth control of crops and some new aspects of how and when to use manure, slurry, fertilizer, lime, water and herbicide.
Features such as 'soil pH', 'soil moisture', 'nutrients' and 'delayed effects' have been added.    
    </description>

